# Owned by the Oracle Adapters HLD (section 2.2 / section 8). Committed in the
# SAME change that creates benchmark/oracles/ so adapter dependency trees can
# never be accidentally committed or CRLF-mangled. Absent on a fresh clone;
# the per-adapter README bootstrap step recreates these and MUST run before
# any oracle invocation or self-test.
*/.venv/
*/node_modules/

# Python bytecode caches produced by running the Trafilatura adapter / its
# self-test. Build artifacts, never deliverables — must not be committed.
*/__pycache__/
*.pyc
